“一切在2月19日之后都变得不一样了”——三个韩国人的疫情感受。
"Everything changed after February 19th" -- the three Koreans felt the epidemic.
“一切在2月19日之后都变得不一样了”——三个韩国人的疫情感受。
"Everything changed after February 19th" -- the three Koreans felt the epidemic.
